values: Okay i have to bitch about something so if you arent into reading a bitchy journal dont continue................ alright there is a couple i know who lives in my building, there son moved down from nova scotia, well they get in a fight and the son was not alowed to stay in there house because they were going away for the week. so i was asked if he could stay with me, cool cool  they were comeing back  friday, well in the middle of the week the dad calls here and was like oh your kicked out and you arent welcome in the house when we get back. okay i am pissed cause one i 18 i let a 17 year old stay with me that i didnt even know then the pooor kid is told he has know where to live while he was staying with me, so what did the dad think he was going to stay with me, i cant afford that ppl need to grow up and stop putting there fucking problems on other ppl, i never got a fucking thank you, even though i called and found out the info on how to get him home, that should have been the fathers job, not only that you dont ask someone to if there kid can stay with you and then when they are with you go oh you have no where to live GERRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRR i will not do anything for anyone besides my family and they few friends that are like family.

We had an awsome time camping, the site itself was a disapointment but thats okay. We didnt have a lake to swim in, well there was a lake more like a swamp but still the was a pool that we spent alot of time in. And since we came back troy has been really nice, and i think it might be because he needed a break from work. I have a job interview at Big Al's tommorow, hope i get it but the shifts are really long

So ya everthing i fixed now, rich and leanne r comeing with my mom home, so everything is great, dont get me wrong i wanted them to come its just like i said i would have cryed over it if they didnt, but since they comeing great, it going to be an awsome time, and anyone who may ruin it i will drowned them in lake. of course i will need help but i am pretty sure jeff help me. lol i love that he is evil. anyways see if i would have listened to jess then they would have been able to go and thats would have been shitty, i not saying he said to just say there isnt enough room to be mean, i now he probably had it in good intentions but still i aint getting in shit for nothing

Gerrrrrrr this camping trip is going so shitty first we have plans set out, then rich car break's down so we have to make new plans. Then rich and leanne dont want to go at all. So we make new plans, then rich and leanne wanna come, this is just pissing me off. I wish we  can stick with one plan. My mom is sapouse to pick us up and if more ppl r comeing then i need to know to ask her if it is okay. I just want everyone to go and we all have a great time. To be honest i dont care if rich and leanne come cause i really dont know them anyway, i am not going to  cry over it if they dont come. But if they do come then great more ppl the better. i just want set plans. that will not change. Today i have to ask my mom if more ppl can come in her car if there is enough room. Jesse wants me to flat out lie and say there isnt enough room and just forget them coeming,cause one theny were not apart of the plans in first place and two because he doesnt want to lose ride over them going. But i want to be honest about it if there is room then they can come with me if there isnt then i truely sorry about the way it turned out. i just dont want ppl mad at me casue in our group of friends shit like that always happens. Someone will say one thing, then change there story to another person. And it seems like its always happen's to me. but i can honestly say there r times were i have done nothing wrong, then i will get in shit cause someone else says something different. I hate that you have to watch how you say things to certain ppl. I'm telling you watch my next entry will be bitching about some bullshit of ppl not getting story's right. It only ever owkrs when the whole group of us r together so knowone can lie latter cause we all there.

This is my first journal on here, a few friends have it so i am checking it out. Not much has been up lately, went to Canada's wonderland with Hope,Chris,Troy(my bf) troy looks like a lobster from being out in sun all day. He had never been on a water slide before so we took him on a few. My lil brother broke his arm yesturday poor guy. Going camping in 2 weeks cant wait. It will be nice to get away for it bit woth my close friends. Not much else to say i write later
